item.title: Hailee Steinfeld - Realistic (Illustrious)
item.description:
Hailee Steinfeld (born December 11, 1996) is an American actress and singer. She had her breakthrough with the western film True Grit (2010), which earned her various accolades, including nominations for an Academy Award and a BAFTA Award.

Steinfeld gained wider recognition for her roles in the Pitch Perfect film series (2015–2017) and The Edge of Seventeen (2016), which earned her a Golden Globe nomination. She also starred in Ender's Game (2013), Begin Again (2013) and Bumblebee (2018). She voiced Gwen Stacy / Spider-Woman in Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse (2018) and its 2023 sequel, and Vi in the Netflix series Arcane (2021–2024). She portrayed Emily Dickinson in the Apple TV+ series Dickinson (2019–2021), and has portrayed Kate Bishop in the Marvel Cinematic Universe since 2021.

This LoRA is only for the realistic Illustrious checkpoints.

item.title: Leslie Bibb (Ca 2000)
item.description: Leslie Bibb is an American actress and model, born on November 17, 1973, in Bismarck, North Dakota. She gained recognition for her role as Brooke McQueen in the teen drama series Popular (1999–2001), which earned her a Teen Choice Award nomination. Bibb has appeared in several Marvel Cinematic Universe productions, portraying journalist Christine Everhart in Iron Man (2008), Iron Man 2 (2010), and What If...? (2021). Her recent work includes roles in Netflix's Jupiter's Legacy (2021) and the satirical comedy-drama series The White Lotus (2025), where she received critical acclaim for her performance as a Southern country club wife. Bibb has been in a long-term relationship with actor Sam Rockwell since 2007, and the two have collaborated on various projects. Known for her versatility and charm, Bibb continues to shine in both television and film.

item.title: Valerie Bertinelli (Ca 1981)
item.description: Valerie Bertinelli is an American actress and television personality, born on April 23, 1960, in Wilmington, Delaware. She rose to fame as Barbara Cooper Royer on the sitcom One Day at a Time (1975–1984), earning two Golden Globe Awards for her performance. Over the years, she has starred in popular shows like Touched by an Angel and Hot in Cleveland. Beyond acting, Bertinelli became a beloved Food Network host, leading shows like Valerie's Home Cooking and Kids Baking Championship. She has also authored several books, including memoirs and cookbooks. Known for her warmth and charm, she continues to captivate audiences both on-screen and off.

item.title: Emily VanCamp (Ca 2005)
item.description: Emily VanCamp is a Canadian actress born on May 12, 1986, in Port Perry, Ontario. She gained widespread recognition for her role as Emily Thorne in the hit TV series Revenge (2011–2015). VanCamp has also starred in other notable shows like Everwood, Brothers & Sisters, and The Resident. In the Marvel Cinematic Universe, she portrays Sharon Carter, appearing in films like Captain America: The Winter Soldier and Civil War. Beyond her acting career, she is married to actor Josh Bowman, her co-star from Revenge, and they share two children. Known for her versatility and grace, VanCamp continues to captivate audiences with her performances.

item.title: Gemini, i2v prompt generator for wan2.1
item.description:
[change logs]

25.03.19/v1.0
Fixed an issue where a single incorrect symbol was present in the LLM prompt. This is a minor change, but it could slightly improve issues that may occur when inputting text in languages other than English. Additionally, the default setting for the stream option has been changed from ON to OFF.

25.03.25/for start-end frame(beta)
kijai workflow
Analyses the start and end images and ultimately generates an appropriate prompt for use in the i2v start-end workflow. However, depending on the image or motion, the end frame may not work properly.

Regarding censorship:
By default, LLM model Gemini has censorship in image analysis. However, by adding a specific part to the prompt to bypass this, I've been able to force the analysis of quite a few images. But if you encounter an error, try deleting the ComfyUI cache (the default location is in the top right of the screen) and trying again.

Using a custom LLM prompt, analyze the image and output the structure as a prompt suitable for the wan2.1 i2v model.

+While it can also be used in Hunyuan, it is recommended to exclude prompts related to camera motion.

Analysis Results - This is a prompt generated by analyzing an image. It signifies the meaning of the image rather than motion.

Image Analysis with Motion - This adds appropriate motion to the generated prompt based on the image.

[Optional] Motion Input - Enter custom motion. The LLM model will refer to what you input.

*You can enter anything as long as it's a language Gemini can understand.

A Gemini API key is required. (FREE)

Also, enter the API key issued in the JSON file located at ComfyUI_windows_portable\ComfyUI\custom_nodes\comfyui-ollamagemini\config.json

Test Generation (v1.0)

Test setting
-Model) wan 2.1 i2v 480p GGUF Q6_K
-LoRA 1) https://civitai.com/models/929497/aesthetic-quality-modifiers-masterpiece?modelVersionId=1498121
-LoRA 2) https://civitai.com/models/1264662/live-wallpaper-style
-480*701, 20steps, 64fps(4sec)

+LoRA was used with trigger words to assist with movement

Analysis Results
A digital painting illustration of an anime pale girl with short white hair decorated with a dark rose on her head and dark angel wings behind her back. She has a red halo with spikes floating above her. She wears a long black dress with gold trim and holds out her hand, with a ring on her finger, as she prepares to cast a spell. The background is a dark gradient of black and red tones. A full shot from a medium perspective.

[Optional] Motion Input
The surrounding blood effects spin around the girl. Her wings gently flutter. Her arms gently wrap around the effects.

Image Analysis with Motion (with Optional Input)
A digital painting of a pale woman with short white hair and piercing red eyes, adorned with a black rose. She stands with a confident posture, her left hand elegantly raised, displaying a delicate gold ring. The woman is dressed in a tight-fitting black dress with gold trim, complemented by matching gold bracelets and thigh-high stockings with floral prints. The surrounding blood effects spin around her. Her wings gently flutter. Her arms gently wrap around the effects. The background features a dark, blurry ambiance with a subtle red glow, enhancing the mysterious atmosphere. The image is a medium shot from a slightly high angle, giving her an imposing look.

Image Analysis with Motion (w/o Optional Input)
A digital painting illustration of an anime pale girl with short white hair decorated with a dark rose on her head and dark angel wings behind her back. She has a red halo with spikes floating above her head. She wears a long black dress with gold trim, a gold bracelet, and long black gloves, revealing a white tattoo on her leg. She holds out her hand, with a gold ring on her finger, as she prepares to cast a spell, her fingers slightly curved and radiating a faint glow. The background is a dark gradient of black and red tones with red energy lines. A full shot from a medium perspective.

Test Generation (for i2v start-end frame)

[Start Image]
A digital art anime illustration of a fair-skinned girl wearing a black and white maid outfit with a light blue bow. Her long, dark blue hair is styled with a side ponytail tied with a black ribbon, and a strand partially covers her right eye. Above her head floats a light blue halo. She sits on a red sofa, her hands resting demurely on her lap. Her bright blue eyes are fully open, and she gazes downward with a melancholic expression. The background is softly blurred with a window hinting at a bright outdoor scene. A medium shot captures her seated posture.

[End Image]
An anime-style illustration of a young girl with black hair, styled in pigtails, sitting on a red sofa. She wears a maid outfit with a white apron and a blue bow tie, complemented by white stockings and wristbands. Her light blue eyes are half open, and she smiles sweetly while making a peace sign with both hands. A halo hovers above her head. The background is softly lit with a window in view, maintaining a clean and bright aesthetic. A medium shot of a seated portrait, capturing her joyful expression and costume details in a smooth, cel-shaded style.

[Final Prompts]
A digital anime-style video prompt showing a girl on a red sofa, transitioning from a melancholic state to a joyful one. Initially, she's depicted as fair-skinned, with long, dark blue hair styled in a side ponytail and a strand partially veiling her right eye. A light blue halo floats above her as she sits demurely, her bright blue eyes cast downward with a melancholic expression, her hands resting gently on her lap. As the video progresses, her eyes gradually open wider, and her lips curve into a sweet smile, all while her dark blue hair subtly lightens to black. Her hands, previously resting, gracefully lift to form a peace sign with both hands. Her halo remains consistently above her head throughout the transition. The background remains a soft blur, with a window suggesting a bright outdoor scene. The camera remains fixed, preserving the medium shot perspective and focusing on the natural evolution of her expression and pose.
